<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You - MyChart | Kaiser Permanente</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: #f5f7fa;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .header {
            background: #0066cc;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .header-content {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .kp-logo {
            background: white;
            color: #0066cc;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .mychart-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .thank-you-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
            border: 1px solid #e1e8ed;
        }

        .success-icon {
            font-size: 64px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            display: block;
        }

        .thank-you-title {
            color: #28a745;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .thank-you-subtitle {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .feedback-highlight {
            background: #e8f5e8;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6c3;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .highlight-title {
            color: #2e7d32;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .highlight-text {
            color: #1b5e20;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .next-steps {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .next-steps h4 {
            color: #0066cc;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .next-steps ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .next-steps li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .next-steps li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: #0066cc;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #004499;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            color: #666;
            border: 1px solid #e1e8ed;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #e9ecef;
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .epic-footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .action-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .container {
                padding: 30px 15px;
            }

            .thank-you-card {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-content">
            <div class="logo-section">
                <div class="kp-logo">KP</div>
                <div class="mychart-title">MyChart</div>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: right; font-size: 14px;">
                <div style="font-weight: 600;">Sarah Johnson</div>
                <div style="font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.9;">Feedback Complete</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="thank-you-card">
            <span class="success-icon">üôè</span>

            <h1 class="thank-you-title">Thank You for Your Feedback!</h1>
            <p class="thank-you-subtitle">
                Your feedback has been successfully submitted and will help us continue to improve 
                the quality of care and services at Kaiser Permanente South Bay.
            </p>

            <div class="feedback-highlight">
                <div class="highlight-title">
                    üìà Your Voice Matters
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-text">
                    Patient feedback is essential to our commitment to providing exceptional healthcare. 
                    Your responses will be reviewed by our quality improvement team and shared with 
                    Dr. Michael Chen to enhance future patient experiences.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h4>What Happens Next?</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>üìã Your feedback will be reviewed within 2-3 business days</li>
                    <li>üìû If you indicated concerns, a patient representative may contact you</li>
                    <li>üìä Your responses contribute to our continuous quality improvement efforts</li>
                    <li>üí° We may use your insights to enhance our AI-powered pre-visit tools</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="/portal" class="btn btn-primary">Return to MyChart Home</a>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Schedule Next Appointment</a>
            </div>

            <div class="epic-footer">
                <div><strong>Kaiser Permanente South Bay Medical Center</strong></div>
                <div style="margin-top: 5px;">Committed to your health and well-being ‚Ä¢ Powered by EPIC MyChart</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>